{"data":[{"id":563884230,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563884230","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546307413,"updated_time":1546311673,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":17,"comment_count":8,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e我们从他自己的思路出发，而不是从他的写法出发说明一下错误之处：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他的原文错误之处在于：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e若 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cexists%7Bn_0%7D%5Cin%5Cmathbb%7BN%7D_%2B%2C2n_0%5Cnotin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"\\exists{n_0}\\in\\mathbb{N}_+,2n_0\\notin{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，则 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1\" alt=\"-1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 不是质数。\u003cbr\u003e当 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n_0%3D1\" alt=\"n_0=1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 时，若 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2%5Cnotin%7BA%7D\" alt=\"2\\notin{A}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，则 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1\" alt=\"-1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 不是质数\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个“\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1\" alt=\"-1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 不是质数”写法虽然是不对的，但是显然我们可以用我们的数学知识来改变他的写法使得“\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1\" alt=\"-1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 不是质数”本身没毛病，也就是我们把“属于A”改为一个关于P集合的谓词，然后“\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=-1\" alt=\"-1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 是质数”改为“P=全体质数 并 {-1}”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那么问题就仅限于一个初学者常见的错误了：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e把(\\exists x,P(x)) \\to Q错误地变换为了\\exists x (P(x) \\to Q)\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"我们从他自己的思路出发，而不是从他的写法出发说明一下错误之处：他的原文错误之处在于：若 \\exists{n_0}\\in\\mathbb{N}_+,2n_0\\notin{A} ，则 -1 不是质数。 当 n_0=1 时，若 2\\notin{A} ，则 -1 不是质数这个“-1 不是质数”写法虽然是不对的，但是显然我…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=24\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%